{"tid":1880731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「相信共產黨」飲雙黃連口服液 江蘇大叔病情加重","createTime":"2020-02-15T05:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T13:00:38.000Z","uid":18348,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e4656817c61e7c1bb6566f7bac9cff19d7309fb9","tid":1880731,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"中國科學院上海藥物所早前聲稱，與武漢病毒所聯合研究初步發現，中成藥「雙黃連口服液」可抑制武漢肺炎病毒，引爆內地人搶購潮，因與當年「急性盲搶鹽」相似，結果淪為網民笑柄。該所一直都拿不出證據，支持相關結論可信，甚至在接受《新京報》採訪時突改口：「不想把話說死。」諷刺的是，江蘇連雲港市一名57歲男子，因仍選擇「相信共產黨」，連續兩天服用雙黃連口服液後，肺炎病情加重。<br />\n<br />\n據《揚子晚報》報道，該名男子上周五（7日）身體出現不適，被兒子接回家中休養。男子因為在媒體上看過中科院推薦雙黃連的療效，便自行服用雙黃連口服液，沒想到病情加重，出現頭暈、胸悶、乾咳等症狀。他周日（9日）被送進醫院，目前隔離治療。<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》曾於上月31日深夜重點推播新聞稱，武漢病毒所與中科院上海藥物的研究團隊透過實驗室「體外試驗」證明，雙黃連有抑制新型冠狀病毒的作用，而引爆搶購。<br />\n雖然中科院後來改口，坦承上述結論未經過臨床驗證，但各大藥房貨架上的雙黃連口服液仍被瘋搶一空，不但網購平台的相關藥品被買到斷貨，連獸藥用的黃連素也被搶購。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200215/NRSVHSTT67Y6FMKKIMZOTGYJLQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2K6LSEZ6wP1s4jJizgSAJy0hGo8Yd5LOWGlIezkr77GI13_1_zbY9Z3rg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200215%2FNRSVHSTT67Y6FMKKIMZOTGYJLQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2K6LSEZ6wP1s4jJizgSAJy0hGo8Yd5LOWGlIezkr77GI13_1_zbY9Z3rg&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=a055bfcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200215%2FNRSVHSTT67Y6FMKKIMZOTGYJLQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2K6LSEZ6wP1s4jJizgSAJy0hGo8Yd5LOWGlIezkr77GI13_1_zbY9Z3rg&h=daa8b5cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200215/NRSVHSTT67Y6FMKKIMZOTGYJLQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2K6LSEZ6wP1s4jJizgSAJy0hGo8Yd5LOWGlIezkr77GI13_1_zbY9Z3rg</a>"},{"pid":"2bd0abee970eb92772cf22b0c153cff9d7bcf65a","tid":1880731,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4a06e0161a4053e9a54dc74adb30bfacd84d0b","tid":1880731,"uid":38154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"信黨得永生<br />\n<br />\nPs.喺地獄永生"},{"pid":"3d36c61e2f607ef6c2a1388740eebe2f7fd3964a","tid":1880731,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:43:14.000Z","msg":"只要人死左,病毒都生存唔到,就唔會有肺炎<br />\n係呢方面信共襄盛舉黨錯唔晒<br />\n手術非常成功，亦可以減少垃圾人口"},{"pid":"4429e287a68d2351283956390d082a4a652410d2","tid":1880731,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"食雙黃蓮蓉月餅就無事啦"},{"pid":"2db9d7b5949c3ae1c90ba686877ad753eec131e5","tid":1880731,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T12:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d23437ddb6f803a18b679f2e44219be2a90a10","tid":1880731,"uid":95360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦<br />\n咁咪可以快d接見毛主席囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0684968b9cd17397b8bccfd1ec1688836a03fed8","tid":1880731,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db95959a41e428dc99bb3955543f4f37698723bf","tid":1880731,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":